criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ＞18 yeas;

          -  Diagnosis of CAP according to the diagnosis and treatment of community-acquired
             pneumonia in adults: 2016 clinical practice guidelines by the Chinese Thoracic
             Society, Chinese Medical Association.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Bronchiectasis;

          -  Active tuberculosis;

          -  Aspiration pneumonia or obstructive pneumonia;

          -  Hospitalized in 2 weeks;

          -  Hospitalized or ventilated ≥5 days;

          -  Severe immunosuppression patients;

          -  Irregular follow-up and lost follow-up;

          -  Withdraw from the study for any reason.
